SCase10.hs:(11,14)-(18,8): Splicing expression
    ghc-internal:GHC.Internal.TH.Quote.quoteExp
      sCase
      " e of\n\
      \               Zero          -> 0\n\
      \               Num k         -> k\n\
      \               Var s         -> ite (s .== literal \"a\") 1 2\n\
      \               Add (Num i) j -> i + t j\n\
